  "description": "<p>分类: <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/category/wearables/\" rel=\"tag\">佩戴产品</a>, <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/category/fitness/\" rel=\"tag\">健康产品</a></p><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/05/29/samsung-launches-a-flexible-platform-of-sensors-for-wearables/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://o.aolcdn.com/hss/storage/midas/28ca6cd0999f493aac6321755345b15f/200176070/simband-4.jpg\" style=\"width: 620px; height: 316px;\" /></a></div>\n\n<div><br />\n在昨晚举行的「Voice of the Body」发布会上，三星推出了一个名为 SIMBAND 的全新模块话可穿戴健康设备参考平台，希望藉此来推进健身产品的发展。上面这张概念图绘制的就是其原型机之一，它内建了多个传感器，比如说可用来侦测皮肤吸光量（最终得到脉搏等数据）的可见光感应器或是集成在腕带上的 ECG（心电图）感应器等。</div><p><br /><p class=\"continueReading\"><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/05/29/samsung-launches-a-flexible-platform-of-sensors-for-wearables/\" rel=\"bookmark\">继续阅读全文 <em>三星推出 SIMBAND 可穿戴健康设备参考平台</em></a></p><h6 style=\"clear: both; padding: 8px 0 0 0; height: 2px; font-size: 1px; border: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"></h6><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/05/29/samsung-launches-a-flexible-platform-of-sensors-for-wearables/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent link to this entry\">此文章网址</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/forward/20894656/\" title=\"Send this entry to a friend via email\">转寄此文章</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/05/29/samsung-launches-a-flexible-platform-of-sensors-for-wearables/#comments\" title=\"View reader comments on this entry\">回应</a><hr size=\"1\" />", 
